cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with sequence generation tasks such as Machine Translation and Image Captioning. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new model for sequence generation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it deals with Image-to-LaTeX and Image Captioning tasks. It may also be relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it proposes a new model for sequence generation using neural networks.
